      World news story
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Information for British citizens in Latvia
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The British Embassy Riga held two meetings on 1 and 2 October to update British citizens living in the country about Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
